Ldapmapper : CRUD objects for LDAP binding and mapping 
This library provide easy access to LDAP objects for read and write actions on Ruby mapping instance on LDAP Objects (LDIF record)

Author   : Romain GEORGES <romain@ultragreen.net>

* Ldapmapper is implemented and for Ruby language :
